g.text: * A 16-bit counter with load and reset control bits.
This register was added to show the state
between two time units. In real world this
might not be required since the clock ticks
continuously. This was added here to sort
of stop the time and peek the state between
contiguous time units. This enables the 'inc'
flag to be the clock signal. From 1 to 0 to 1,
